{"tid":1124381,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《殺神John Wick 3》MCL限量版戲票 送Fucking Pencil一枝","createTime":"2019-04-25T04:11:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-27T04:06:12.000Z","uid":41343,"like":228,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":63,"replies":[{"pid":"925e0f1a21ba131edeb9dd10c81a6f7dfbcfae5d","tid":1124381,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T04:11:35.000Z","msg":"【超限量．全城追「殺」】《殺神John Wick 3》限量版殺手套票 <br />\n.<br />\n4月26日起，MCL獨家發售，追殺價 $167（每人限買兩套，售完即止）。<br />\n詳情請向MCL戲院票房職員查詢。<br />\n.<br />\n內附：<br />\n1.      殺神JOHN WICK鉛筆1枝<br />\n2.      殺神JOHN WICK明信片2張<br />\n3.      CONTINENTAL酒店電影卡1張 <br />\n     (附戲票二維碼，可換取《殺神John Wick 3》戲票乙張)<br />\n.<br />\n條款及細則：<br />\n＊ 此套票只售賣給18歲或以上人士<br />\n＊    發售地點： Festival Grand Cinema、皇室戲院、康怡戲院、MCL長沙灣戲院、Movie Town - 新城市廣場<br />\n＊    憑卡上之二維碼到全線MCL戲院可換取《殺神John Wick 3》戲票乙張（不適用於BEA Festival Suite 、Onyx Cinema LED、RealD Cinema (3D)及 MX4D）<br />\n＊    只適用於《殺神John Wick 3》放映期間之場次，逾期無效<br />\n＊    不可兌換現金<br />\n＊    圖片只供參考，禮品外型及顏色以實物為準<br />\n＊    如個別戲院因進行裝修而暫停營業或租約期滿，閣下仍可於其他指定MCL戲院換取《殺神John Wick 3》戲票<br />\n＊    如有任何爭議，洲立影片發行(香港)有限公司及MCL戲院保留最終決定權<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3tFM4ys.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3tFM4ys.jpg&h=250144e2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b3ce351a5a0a23718004bd9d4d375f02f3cdff25","tid":1124381,"uid":55924,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T04:12:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"143c007e208c4afc3e3f5298b6fa45e46a408fbf","tid":1124381,"uid":15211,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T04:12:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef1e9aa29435aecb00ffc0deb44883bb759345a8","tid":1124381,"uid":82845,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,